OL,4,Cresuscitate' notice of the wrong
OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FThe heartbroken son of a retired nurse
OL,8,Fhas said she "dedicated her life to
OL,9,Fthe NHS" and "failed when she needed
OL,10,Fit most".
OL,12,FPat Dawson died after medical staff at
OL,13,Fhospital in Blackburn used the wrong
OL,14,Fnotes which requested the patient
OL,15,Fshould not be resuscitated if they
OL,16,Fwere seriously unwell.
OL,18,FStaff stopped giving the 73-year-old
OL,19,FCPR which resulted in her death.
