OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FHer son, John, said: "Not once in the
OL,8,Flast 30 years had mum personally
OL,9,Fsought any kind of emergency NHS care,
OL,10,Fthat is until the tragic circumstances
OL,11,Fwe have re-lived here today.
OL,13,F"And tragic is truly what it is. It is
OL,14,Fbeyond belief quite how
OL,15,Fcatastrophically she was failed not by
OL,16,Fone individual but by the NHS trust.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
