OL,3,CMum died after medics checked 'do not
OL,4,Cresuscitate' notice of the wrong
OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,F"Life will not be the same without mum
OL,8,Fand we cannot bring her back, but we
OL,9,Fwould be failing as a family if we
OL,10,Fdidn't highlight how much room for
OL,11,Fimprovement there is at the Royal
OL,12,FBlackburn Hospital emergency
OL,13,Fdepartment."
OL,15,FPat was taken to hospital by ambulance
OL,16,Fwith a suspected bowel obstruction on
OL,17,F19 September last year, the court
OL,18,Fheard.
