OL,7,FThat night, the accident and emergency
OL,8,Fdepartment had been categorised as
OL,9,F"over capacity and over-stretched" an
OL,10,Fhour before she arrived with John.
OL,12,FThere were more than 90 patients
OL,13,Fwaiting to be seen, the inquest was
OL,14,Ftold.
OL,16,FAs John sat with his mother after she
OL,17,Fhad been pronounced dead he was
OL,18,Fvisited by a senior nurse who informed
OL,19,Fhim of the mistake.
