OL,3,CMum died after medics checked 'do not
OL,4,Cresuscitate' notice of the wrong
OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that staff had
OL,8,Ffailed to check the NHS number on
OL,9,FPat's wristband or even by confirming
OL,10,Fthe gender and age on the notes.
OL,12,FGiving evidence to the inquest,
OL,13,Femergency consultant Dr Ahmad Alabood
OL,14,Fsaid it had been an "honest mistake
OL,15,Fbecause (staff) were rushing".
OL,17,FDr Alabood said that, when Pat was
OL,18,Fbrought into A&E, the department was
OL,19,F'significantly over-stretched and over-
OL,20,Fcrowded'.
