OL,4,Cresuscitate' notice of the wrong
OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FAll eight bays in resus were full and
OL,8,Feach nurse had an unlimited number of
OL,9,Fpatients to look after.
OL,11,FDr Alabood admitted that it is
OL,12,Fprobable that Pat would have been
OL,13,Fresuscitated had medics attempted to
OL,14,Fdo so.
OL,16,FIn his statement read out during the
OL,17,Finquest, Pat's son John said: "I know
OL,18,Fthat our mum will have been horrified
OL,19,Fby how the system she gave her life to
OL,20,Ffailed her at her time of greatest
OL,21,Fneed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
