OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,F"It is beyond belief the catastrophic
OL,8,Fway in which she was failed, not only
OL,9,Fby one individual but by doctors who
OL,10,Fhave sworn the Hippocratic oath to do
OL,11,Fno harm and our mum paid the ultimate
OL,12,Fprice."
OL,14,FThe Royal Blackburn Hospital said
OL,15,Fseveral systemic changes have been
OL,16,Fimplemented since Pat's death and
OL,17,Fafter an internal investigation.
