OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FThese include limiting the number of
OL,8,Fpatients each nurse looks after to
OL,9,Ffive and reactivating a DNR every
OL,10,Fthree months.
OL,12,FA post mortem CT scan confirmed the
OL,13,Fcause of Pat's death was aspiration
OL,14,Fpneumonitis after she inhaled stomach
OL,15,Fcontents which was caused by a small
OL,16,Fbowel obstruction.
