OL,5,Cpatient
OL,7,FReturning a narrative conclusion, the
OL,8,Fcoroner flagged up several areas of
OL,9,F"sub-standard care" which Pat had
OL,10,Freceived including a failure to record
OL,11,Fany of the tests carried out in
OL,12,Fhospital, not following the sepsis and
OL,13,Fabdominal pathways and the error in
OL,14,Fchecking the wrong patient's notes.
OL,16,FThe coroner concluded that Pat would
OL,17,Fnot have died when she did had it not
OL,18,Fbeen for the mistakes and,
OL,19,Fsignificantly, made a ruling of
OL,20,Fneglect.
